Six-Warrior Quests


Six-Warrior Quests are quests undertaken by a party of six allies. Allies can be subbed into battle as the situation requires to tackle fearsome foes.
*Call abilities may be set for each of the six allies.
■ Facing Six-Warrior Quests

The following condition must be met before taking on six-warrior quests.
• At least six allies must be both level 90 and crystal strength 90.
■ Rewards in Six-Warrior Quests

The following items are the principal rewards in six-warrior quests.

• Providence Cores
Used to cast and sublimate ultima weapons. Clearing each area to awards 100.

• Force Stone Fragments
Used to raise allies' force levels. Required from a certain level. Each area cleared to awards 40.
■ The Crystal Icon
Your progress in clearing six-warrior quests is represented by a crystal icon grade.
Grade conditions change as new areas are added, so your grade may change at that time as well.
E.g.:
A crystal icon grade of 2★ before new areas are added may become 1★ after the areas are added.
*Refer to the Six-Warrior Quests notices for more details.
